$ Excel: Formulas -> Formula Auditing -> Show Formulas

Toggle the display of → Microsoft/Office/Excel/formulas[formulas] in a → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/Worksheet.

With → development/languages/VBA, this display can be toggled using the
→ Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/WorksheetView#excel-worksheetView-display-properties[`.displayFormulas`] property of the → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/WorksheetView[`worksheetView` object].
